OL,3,C'Disgraceful political choice': Waspi
OL,4,Cwomen denied compensation for second
OL,5,Ctime
OL,7,FThe government has apologised over
OL,8,Fwomen not being sent individual
OL,9,Fletters about changes to the state
OL,10,Fpension age, but said they would not
OL,11,Fbe compensated. ITV News Political
OL,12,FCorrespondent Harry Horton reports
OL,14,FThe government has re-affirmed its
OL,15,Fdecision not to compensate women who
OL,16,Fwere affected by the way changes to
OL,17,Fthe state pension age were
OL,18,Fcommunicated.
