OL,7,FWomen Against State Pension Inequality
OL,8,F(Waspi) has campaigned for support for
OL,9,Fwomen born in the 1950s, saying they
OL,10,Fdid not receive sufficient warning of
OL,11,Fthe state pension age for women being
OL,12,Fraised from 60 to 65, in line with men.
OL,14,FThose affecrted were initially told
OL,15,Fthey would not receive state pension
OL,16,Fcompensation in December 2024.
