OL,7,FIn November last year, Work and
OL,8,FPensions Secretary Pat McFadden said
OL,9,Fthe government would reconsider this
OL,10,Fdecision after the emergence of new
OL,11,F"evidence" which his predecessor Liz
OL,12,FKendall was not shown.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
