OL,3,C'Disgraceful political choice': Waspi
OL,4,Cwomen denied compensation for second
OL,5,Ctime
OL,7,FBut on Thursday, McFadden told the
OL,8,FCommons: "The evidence shows that the
OL,9,Fvast majority of 1950s-born women
OL,10,Falready knew the state pension age was
OL,11,Fincreasing thanks to a wide range of
OL,12,Fpublic information, including through
OL,13,Fleaflets, education campaigns,
OL,14,Finformation in GP surgeries, on TV,
OL,15,Fradio, cinema and online.
OL,17,F"To specifically compensate only those
OL,18,Fwomen who suffered injustice would
OL,19,Frequire a scheme that could reliably
OL,20,Fverify the individual circumstances of
OL,21,Fmillions of women."
