OL,7,FMcFadden apologised that women were
OL,8,Fnot sent individual letters about
OL,9,Fchanges to the state pension, but
OL,10,Freiterated the government's decision.
OL,12,FA Parliamentary and Health Service
OL,13,FOmbudsman report has previously
OL,14,Fsuggested compensation between #1,000
OL,15,Fto nearly #3,000 could be suitable for
OL,16,Fthose affected by how the changes were
OL,17,Fcommunicated.
