OL,7,FWaspi chairwoman Angela Madden
OL,8,Fresponded to the government's
OL,9,Fdecision, saying: "Ministers have
OL,10,Fdemonstrated their utter contempt for
OL,11,F1950s-born women, for parliament and
OL,12,Ffor the parliamentary ombudsman.
OL,14,F"The government has kicked the can
OL,15,Fdown the road for months, only to
OL,16,Farrive at exactly the same conclusion
OL,17,Fit has always wanted to.
