OL,3,C'Disgraceful political choice': Waspi
OL,4,Cwomen denied compensation for second
OL,5,Ctime
OL,7,F"This is a disgraceful political
OL,8,Fchoice by a small group of very
OL,9,Fpowerful people, who have decided the
OL,10,Fharm and injustice suffered by
OL,11,Fmillions of ordinary women simply does
OL,12,Fnot matter."
OL,14,FShe insisted that Waspi will continue
OL,15,Fto fight for financial compensation.
OL,17,FPolitical opponents have also
OL,18,Fchallenged the government's decision.
