OL,7,FConservative Mark Garnier criticised
OL,8,Fthe Labour government for turning on
OL,9,Fthe Waspi women.
OL,11,FHe said: "No wonder therefore that the
OL,12,FWaspi women, who were promised so
OL,13,Fmuch, are so angry.
OL,15,F"The people who used to stand beside
OL,16,Fthem have turned against them. If the
OL,17,Fgovernment really believed that these
OL,18,Fwomen had faced a great injustice,
OL,19,Fthey would have found a way to
OL,20,Fcompensate them."
