OL,7,FSteve Darling, the Lib Dem's work and
OL,8,Fpensions spokesman, said: "There are
OL,9,Fmore than 3.6 million Waspi women
OL,10,Facross the UK who will feel this as if
OL,11,Fit were a punch in the stomach.
OL,13,F"They will feel utterly betrayed, and
OL,14,Fthey will feel betrayed because false
OL,15,Fhope was given to them in the autumn,
OL,16,Fand so that hope has been dashed."
