OL,7,FCriticism has not just come from
OL,8,Fpolitical opponents though.
OL,10,FLabour's Rebecca Long Bailey said: "It
OL,11,Fis frankly wrong that the Government
OL,12,Fhas once again chosen to reject
OL,13,Fcompensation for the 1950s women
OL,14,Faffected by state pension age changes."
OL,16,FIn 1995, the government announced
OL,17,Fwomen's state pension age would be
OL,18,Fincreased in phases from 2010 over ten
OL,19,Fyears.
